b'Zan Sayonara Zetsubou Sensei': b"Nozomu Itoshiki is still the bizarre teacher of the even stranger Class 2-F. With more students and friends than before, Zetsubo-sensei's life becomes harder and crazier than ever before.\n\n(Source: ANN)"
